data.title: City of Belleville Awarded Grant from American Water Charitable Foundation
data.meta_description: The City of Belleville has been awarded a $109,000 Building Better Communities grant from the American Water Charitable Foundation/National Recreation and Park Association for the Bellevue Park Nature Play Area. See the press release here!
